data.title: Indiana Needs More Attention #38
data.description:
Presented By Fleet Farm
Check out Charlie's New Stand Up Special "Midwest Goodbye" on YouTube
Our first caller is considering a career change and has a passion for the art of wood carving. Next caller has been in a committed relationship with her boyfriend for nearly two decades, and is wondering if he'll ever propose. Charlie and Myles discuss some possible ways on getting him to propose. Lastly, we've got a caller who's uncorked some wine in her closet and is feeling a bit wined up about why Indiana isn't getting the attention it deserves.
